Phase 10: Ultimate Orchestration & Multi-VLC Expansion
This phase evolves the workstation's parsing engine into a high-fidelity forensic orchestrator. "Ultimate Mode" will now force execution of all available parsers, bypass category filtering, and generate separate serialized JSON dumps for deep analysis. We also introduce a tri-profile VLC system for redundant verification.

User Review Required
IMPORTANT

Storage & Performance: "Ultimate Mode" will generate additional files (JSON dumps) in a new data/forensic_exports/ directory. This mode is resource-intensive and intended for deep-dive investigations.

VLC Tri-Mode: We will implement vlc_quick, vlc_standard, and vlc_deep as distinct steps in the chain. This provides triple redundancy for tricky formats as requested.

